description: This file defines the interface for a plugin main component, including function declarations for initializing, checking support, and unloading the plugin. It contains macro definitions, include guards, and C linkage specifications.

methods.name: COSA_Init
methods.description: Initializes the plugin with a maximum version supported and plugin info pointer.

methods.name: COSA_IsObjSupported
methods.description: Checks if a specific object is supported by the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_Unload
methods.description: Performs cleanup and unloads the plugin.
